{"title":"握手不分开","authors":["傅占元"],"dates":[{"year":1960,"month":4,"day":7}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"握手不分开"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"郑州热电厂工人　傅占元"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"真叫人心焦，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"真叫人急坏，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"浇麦的水泵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"怎么也转不起来！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不要心焦，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不要急坏，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你看工人抗旱大队，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"浩浩荡荡地走来……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这个老电工，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一下子就检查出毛病来，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"原来是——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"接错了线圈。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"接好线圈，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"又重新装起来，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"再把电钮按，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"哈！水泵哗哗地打水叫人真痛快！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"哈！真痛快，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"哈！真痛快，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"眼睛对着眼睛笑，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"工农握手不分开……"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}